#, no-wrap
msgid "DIRECTION"
msgstr "DIRECTION"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/firewalls/_index.adoc:1963
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Next, each rule must explicitly state the direction of traffic using one of "
